    public class UrbanizationsTreatmentSimulatedServiceImpl
extends Object
implements UrbanizationsTreatmentService, UrbanizationsTreatmentSimulatedService
    Interface UrbanizationsTreatmentService implementation. This service, that we will add by composition to the implementation of the driver, simulates all the logic that an authentic service should do that it will consult by coordinates in GoogleMaps or something similar.
